flowRoot.flowPara: Talk about expectations for the group to draw in participation from all group members and help craft group identity. It’s okay if not everybody agrees on everything!

flowPara.flowSpan: First: Ask learners how they want to work with their peers in the coming weeks.Prompt learners with these questions:·

flowRoot.flowPara: · Do you want to work through activities on a projector or work on their own?· · Do you want to commit to doing work outside of the Learning Circle?· · Do you feel like you have enough time to complete the course?• Next: Based on the discussion create a list of expectations for their group and discussthe list, leaving room for last minute additions and any disagreements.• Finally: Once the list is final, read the final list to the group.
